;; FINDING 001 (differential harness, corpus 20_guard_raise, hand-shrunk)
;; The value bound by a guard clause after (raise 'boom) is garbage, and the
;; garbage DIFFERS per execution path:
;;   jit (run-cache on) : ()
;;   jit ESHKOL_JIT_CACHE=0 : raw pointer bits, e.g. 4307392536
;;   aot -O0            : () (or #<unknown> in the two-guard variant)
;; Expected (R7RS): boom
;; Axis pairs that diverge: jit-vs-jit-nocache, jit-nocache-vs-aot-o0.
(display (guard (e (#t e)) (raise 'boom)))
(newline)
